# Additional notes
notes: >
  This project includes formal mathematical definitions, theorem proofs,
  engineering best practices, and comprehensive comparisons of stream
  processing systems. It serves as a supplementary resource to official
  documentation, focusing on theoretical foundations and deep understanding
  rather than operational guides.
